content.html: I think it would work better as a panel show, where David Tennant and Peter Capaldi are team captains. On David's team, it's Catherine Tate, Camille Coduri and Bernard Cribbins. On Peter's, it's Jenna Coleman, Michelle Gomez and Matt Lucas. Title: Have I Got Who For You.
